\begin_layout Enumerate
Battery life is crucial if one is to have large classes and offer this in
 Indian government schools.
 Most of the devices cited above need to be charged once a day or once a
 week.
 We felt that one year is the minimum time between changing batteries for
 our requirement for government schools.
 Our experience is that batteries will last about 2 years in our current
 product.
